room_title: Escape room "Motherboard" by Xscape The Room in Philadelphia
room_description: In this espionage adventure, you and your team are part of the “resistance” posing as the maintenance crew tasked to break into the headquarters of a corporate giant, MEGAZON. Locate the supercomputer Motherboard and end her program before she takes over the minds and souls of planet earth. To free the world from her clutches you will have to act quick. You’ll have one hour to accomplish this difficult and dangerous task.
